name: Treachery of Images ReImagined (from the Magritte Reimagined collection)
description: This is a collection that takes the work of surrealist Rene Magritte and reimagines it as photographs. The subjects are replaced with people of color and the inanimate objects are replaced with classic cameras. This is a play on the classic C'est Ne Pas Un Pipe image. I replaced the pipe with a classic rangefinder camera.
